node.text: This spooky season, @bacardiusa and I brought their “Haunted Rum” to life. I kicked off my #Halloween by pranking @MackWilds with the NEW @bacardiusa limited-edition, glow-in-the-dark bottle at their Haunted Rum Bar. Swipe up to see how it unfolds and stop by your local spirits store to grab a limited-edition spooky bottle of your own! #HauntedbyBacardi #DoWhatMovesYou #BacardiPartner

node.text:
A home feels empty to me without art. To express my style and vision, @nikkichuhome curated an
assortment of artwork from @OneKingsLane's extensive catalogue. My favorite piece is a photograph by Drew Doggett entitled Untitled 2: Omo. I love art that celebrates Black culture, and it's a stunning piece that symbolizes strength, power, and perseverance. Every piece of art within my new home brought life to the space and I'm so excited to share them all. 🖤🖤🖤

#OneKingsLane #MyOKLStyle
Photography: @Pippa_Drummond

node.text:
I recently moved into a beautiful brownstone and knew this was this perfect time to call on my friend and interior designer @nikkichuhome to bring this space to life with help from @zgallerie ❤️My style is modern, glam, and a little edgy, and I wanted this space to reflect that while still feeling like a relaxed environment where I can unwind. I truly loved working
with Z Gallerie - everything in my home came together perfectly, and they knew exactly how to capture my style. I can't wait to share the rest of the rooms that Nikki and the ZG team worked on! #zgallerie #zgalleriemoment #zgalleriepartner #gifted
Photography: @pippa_drummond
